{"tid":1365593,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人寫信去比外國警察 叫佢地唔好同黑警進行任何交流/合作","createTime":"2019-07-25T16:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T16:48:36.000Z","uid":261645,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"809aa53f25d58d72e2fc0db77a671b8457cbf35c","tid":1365593,"uid":261645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:33:59.000Z","msg":"我係P 第一次開po 屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警黑合作其實係國際新聞 我地可以再幫佢地傳開去<br />\n一人一封email去外國執法機構 講返元朗發生咩事 並呼籲佢地唔好同黑警進行任何交流/合作 令外國警察都反佢地 恥與港共黑警為伍<br />\n<br />\n但小弟英文差 寫唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人英文勁可以幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792908f69f69cae2a6b07689d3f9b85c5c1acf5f","tid":1365593,"uid":261645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:34:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61d2a865d74d1218f32173859d8a3e8dfff43386","tid":1365593,"uid":261645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:34:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0acaf0ac605eafd27197072e4aab9de4bd38fbfa","tid":1365593,"uid":261645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:34:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"da778beb2c822446cd63131f4f7a5e3901c190cf","tid":1365593,"uid":261645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:34:56.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"ce5796633629ddf35a9450d681f31fca914d2a63","tid":1365593,"uid":261645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:35:06.000Z","msg":"又推"},{"pid":"42e27abf5e4e56e90d603bb0a3e3c58ab45a090d","tid":1365593,"uid":261645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:35:21.000Z","msg":"又再推"},{"pid":"c5b59e1c4bd3a07f5cb91994f0628850e443aeb6","tid":1365593,"uid":261645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T1